<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Elvis — Future Associate</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="fonts.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="mobile.css">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --black: #000000;
    --white: #f0ede8;
    --pink: #ec008d;
    --grey: #2a2a2a;
    --mid: #888;
    --font-display: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif;
    --font-mono: 'Courier Prime', monospace;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--black);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.97);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    text-decoration: none;
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    top: 6px;
  }

  .nav-logo img {
    height: 62px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
    mix-blend-mode: screen;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    list-style: none;
    position: relative;
    top: 8px;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--pink); }

  /* HERO — POSTER FULL BLEED */
  .project-hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 600px;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .project-hero-img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    filter: saturate(0.7) brightness(0.6);
  }

  .project-hero-gradient {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.97) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 50%, rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 100%);
  }

  .project-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    padding: 0 3rem 5rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .project-back {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.25em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .project-back:hover { color: var(--pink); }
  .project-back::before { content: '←'; color: var(--pink); }

  .project-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pink);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 12rem);
    line-height: 0.88;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .project-meta-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .project-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  /* VIDEO */
  .video-section {
    padding: 0 3rem;
    background: var(--black);
  }

  .video-embed {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%;
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .video-embed iframe {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  /* DIVIDER */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--grey), transparent);
    margin: 0 3rem;
  }

  /* BODY CONTENT */
  .project-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.8fr;
    gap: 0;
    min-height: 50vh;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey);
  }

  /* LEFT — DETAILS */
  .project-details {
    padding: 6rem 4rem 6rem 3rem;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--grey);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .detail-block {}

  .detail-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .detail-value {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.8);
  }

  .detail-value strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .role-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .role-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
    border: 1px solid var(--grey);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.8rem;
  }

  /* RIGHT — EDITORIAL */
  .project-editorial {
    padding: 6rem 5rem;
  }

  .editorial-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .editorial-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: rgba(240,237,232,0.75);
    max-width: 620px;
  }

  .editorial-body p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .editorial-body strong {
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    padding: 6rem 3rem 5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
  }

  .footer-location {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mid);
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .project-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .project-details { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--grey); padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .project-editorial { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    .project-hero-content { padding: 0 2rem 4rem; }
    .video-section { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    .divider { margin: 0 1.5rem; }
    nav { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="index.html#reel">Reel</a></li>
    <li><a href="index.html#projects">Projects</a></li>
    <li><a href="about.html">Leadership</a></li>
    <li><a href="careers.html">Careers</a></li>
    <li><a href="contact.html">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
  <button class="nav-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu"><span></span><span></span><span></span></button>
  <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo"><img src="assets/fa_on_black_crop.jpg" alt="Future Associate"></a>
</nav>

<div id="page-content">

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="project-hero">
  <img class="project-hero-img" src="assets/elvis.jpg" alt="Elvis">
  <div class="project-hero-gradient"></div>
  <div class="project-hero-content">
    <a href="index.html#projects" class="project-back">All Projects</a>
    <div class="project-eyebrow">Film · Warner Bros. · 2022</div>
    <h1 class="project-title">Elvis</h1>
    <div class="project-meta-row">
      <div class="project-meta-item">
        <span class="meta-label">Director</span>
        <span class="meta-value">Baz Luhrmann</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-meta-item">
        <span class="meta-label">VFX Supervisor</span>
        <span class="meta-value">Lindsay Adams</span>
      </div>
      <div class="project-meta-item">
        <span class="meta-label">Studio</span>
        <span class="meta-value">Warner Bros.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- VIDEO -->
<div class="video-section">
  <div class="video-embed">
    <iframe
      src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1169769347?autoplay=0&muted=1&loop=0"
      title="Elvis — Future Associate VFX"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
      allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider" style="margin-top: 4rem;"></div>

<!-- BODY -->
<div class="project-body">

  <!-- LEFT: DETAILS -->
  <div class="project-details">

    <div class="detail-block">
      <div class="detail-label">Production</div>
      <div class="detail-value">
        <strong>Elvis</strong><br>
        Warner Bros. Pictures · 2022<br>
        Directed by Baz Luhrmann
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <div class="detail-label">FA Role</div>
      <div class="role-tags">
        <span class="role-tag">VFX Production</span>
        <span class="role-tag">Environment Extension</span>
        <span class="role-tag">Crowd Simulation</span>
        <span class="role-tag">Period Restoration</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="detail-block">
      <div class="detail-label">Links</div>
      <div class="detail-value">
        <a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3704428/" target="_blank" style="color:var(--white); text-decoration:underline; text-decoration-color:var(--pink); text-underline-offset:3px;">IMDB →</a><br>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wBDLRvjHVOY" target="_blank" style="color:var(--white); text-decoration:underline; text-decoration-color:var(--pink); text-underline-offset:3px; margin-top:0.5rem; display:inline-block;">Official Trailer →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- RIGHT: EDITORIAL -->
  <div class="project-editorial">
    <div class="editorial-heading">The Work.</div>
    <div class="editorial-body">
      <p>Baz Luhrmann's <strong>Elvis</strong> demanded a level of visual ambition that matched the man himself. Future Associate was engaged to deliver a suite of VFX sequences spanning the full arc of Elvis Presley's career — from the raw energy of early Tupelo performances through to the spectacular excess of his Las Vegas residency.</p>

      <p>Our work centred on <strong>large-scale environment extensions and period-accurate crowd simulation</strong>, transforming Queensland locations into 1950s American South backdrops and filling the International Hotel with thousands of digital extras. Every frame required forensic attention to period detail — architecture, signage, costume, lighting — to hold up against Luhrmann's hyperkinetic visual style.</p>

      <p>Working alongside Production VFX Supervisor <strong>Lindsay Adams</strong>, the Future Associate team embedded directly with the production pipeline, turning around complex shots under the compressed schedules that blockbuster post demands. The result: seamless work that holds up in one of the most visually scrutinised films of 2022.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-location">Sydney, NSW &nbsp;·&nbsp; Australia</div>
  <div class="footer-copy">© Future Associate Pty Ltd · All Rights Reserved</div>
</footer>

</div>
<script src="transitions.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
